{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In Selenetrope, you\u2019ll navigate a vast network of interconnected interiors full of secrets and mysterious ancient structures, all while being pursued by a multitude of creatures from among the living, the dead, and the incomprehensible in between. Discover new items and abilities that grant you unique ways to explore the world. Venture into the dark and brave the horrors that lurk within to return to your lost home.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Decide how to approach each monster encounter in your own way. You can stealthily sneak by to avoid detection, moving swiftly and quietly. Or, uncover and exploit their weaknesses to gain the advantage. Or, if all else fails, run as fast as you can.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234110/extras/Backwalker2.gif?t=1733847105\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Discover and master the enigmatic structures hidden in the labyrinth's forgotten corners. Reveal their secrets and learn what they are and where they might lead you.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234110/extras/mystery.gif?t=1733847105\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Find new ways to engage with the world that enable you to reach areas previously inaccessible to you. Certain locations feature unique mechanics that may complicate navigation but at the same time offer rewards and opportunity to those who can master them.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\